thread.title: Trevor Bowen
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Trevor Bowen

author: Trevor Bowen
title: Trevor Bowen
text: I highly recommend Ink Station for their high standard of service and fast turn around, together with great quality products. Affordability is critical in the market place. This combined with the high quality of goods delivered and after sales service. Where else would you go?
